author: sussman
msg: Be less conservative about calling the conflict-callback on prop conflicts.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/props.c

a base_file to the callback anyway.

author: pburba
msg: Some code cleanup and doc string improvement in libsvn_client/merge.c.
* subversion/libsvn_client/merge.c
(get_mergeinfo_paths): Clarify doc string, simplify argument list (target
doesn't need to be passed separately, it's already in merge_cmd_baton), and
use only one code path to create svn_client__merge_path_t * for
merge_cmd_baton->target rather than the confusing two we had before.
(discover_and_merge_children): Update call to get_mergeinfo_paths().
